comment.author: 26105073@N03
comment._content: "This Hawker Sea Fury T Mk.20 was delivered in 1957 as VZ368 and transferred to the Burmese Air Force as UB-451. Frank Sanders obtained the fairly complete airframe from Burma and had the aircraft stored in its wooden shipping crate at the family's Chino, California, hangar during 1979........" read more at www.sandersaircraft.com/aircraft_dreadnought.asp
